And now without moving our body we just 
 want to move our hands like this.

00:00:51.177 --> 00:00:59.048
And with the new rules being a little more lenient with 
 overhead passing, I teach, I call it “campfires” 

00:00:59.048 --> 00:01:00.465
so we are warming our hands by a campfire right here. 

00:01:00.465 --> 00:01:04.900
Halfway between passing the ball underhand and passing the ball overhand. 

00:01:05.178 --> 00:01:06.572
So my arm are hanging out here

