Okay. So let’s do a couple of practice passes.

00:07:20.947 --> 00:07:22.660
There you go. Pass and hold.

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:28.540
Pass and hold. There were go. So, you want to 
 avoid any kind of big swinging motions. 

00:07:28.540 --> 00:07:31.980
You kind of want to think about pushing the 
 ball, more than swinging at the ball. 

